Apache_Commons

To be built from source, Kleene needs

commons-lang3-3.1-bin.tar.gz

For licence information, see kleene-lang/NOTICE.

See kleene-lang/tools/README
for the easy way to install this library and make
it accessible to Kleene.

***** below are notes, not instructions

In kleene-lang/tools/Apache_Commons/
there needs to be a link to a copy of 
commons-lang3-3.1-bin.tar.gz
on your system.

If the easy way is not possible or convenient,
the Apache Commons library commons-lang3-3.1-bin.tar.gz
can be downloaded 
from
	http://commons.apache.org/lang/download_lang.cgi
to
kleene-lang/tools/Apache_Commons/


